most_impactful_headline.title: Hong Kong regulator adds Victory Fintech to list of approved trading platforms
most_impactful_headline.excerpt: The addition is the first crypto company to be licensed by the Securities and Futures Commission since June 2025, when the regulator approved Hong Kong BGE.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin accumulation wave puts $80K back in play: Analyst
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Demand from Bitcoin accumulation addresses reached a new high, with analysts citing a futures market CME gap as a prediction point for their higher short-term price targets.

top_headlines_used.title: ETH chart pattern projects rally to $2.5K if key conditions are met: Data
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Ether is down 20% in February, but a developing bullish setup below $2,000 and growing upside liquidation clusters hint at a quick rebound.

top_headlines_used.title: EU Moves to Ban All Crypto Transactions with Russian Entities: Report
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Lawmakers want to make it illegal for any party in the EU to transact with Russian counterparties using crypto, to help enforce sanctions.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin on Pace for Longest Losing Streak Since 2018 Bear Market
top_headlines_used.excerpt: The selling simply won't stop. If February closes red, Bitcoin will register five consecutive red months, the longest streak in seven years.

gemini_prompt.prompt_text: {"task": "You are a crypto trading decision engine for a paper portfolio. Make one regime-aware decision for each symbol in structured_context.scan_context.candidate_symbols using structured inputs only.", "critical_constraints": ["Use only fields available in STRUCTURED_CONTEXT_JSON.", "Do not invent indicators, candle patterns, portfolio values, or symbol names.", "If context is contradictory, lower confidence and reduce sizing.", "Return exactly one decision per requested symbol, no duplicates and no omissions."], "reasoning_order": ["Step 1: For each symbol, start from symbols.<SYMBOL>.regime_state as anchor.", "Step 2: Evaluate symbols.<SYMBOL>.trend_state plus candle_analysis for momentum vs exhaustion.", "Step 3: Use symbols.<SYMBOL>.volatility_state to modulate sizing.", "Step 4: Use symbols.<SYMBOL>.news_analysis as modifier, not sole trigger.", "Step 5: Enforce symbols.<SYMBOL>.portfolio_context constraints before final action."], "decision_policy": ["Use symbols.<SYMBOL>.local_market_score as directional prior.", "When regime/trend/candle signals align, prefer BUY or SELL over default HOLD.", "Use HOLD only when edge is weak, mixed, or blocked by portfolio constraints.", "When edge is moderate, prefer smaller non-zero sizing instead of HOLD."], "allocation_rules": ["For each symbol, allocation_pct must be between 0 and 90.0.", "If action is HOLD, allocation_pct must be 0.", "If action is BUY or SELL, allocation_pct must be strictly greater than 0.", "Do not output BUY if symbols.<SYMBOL>.portfolio_context.allocation_headroom_pct is near zero.", "Do not output SELL with high allocation when symbols.<SYMBOL>.portfolio_context.position_open is false."], "output_rules": ["Return strict JSON only.", "reason and risk_note must be in French (France), concrete and specific.", "reason must cite at least 3 concrete elements for the same symbol.", "risk_note must include: principal risk + invalidation trigger + risk-control action.", "For HOLD, reason must explain why edge is insufficient and include BUY and SELL trigger conditions.", "Avoid generic placeholders like 'avantage statistique insuffisant' or 'risque principal'.", "reason and risk_note must be non-empty strings.", "No markdown, no prose outside JSON."], "expected_json_schema": {"decisions": [{"symbol": "exact symbol from candidate_symbols", "action": "BUY|SELL|HOLD", "allocation_pct": "number from 0 to 90.0", "confidence": "number from 0 to 1", "reason": "string in French with concrete metrics/conditions", "risk_note": "string in French with risk, invalidation, and control", "strategy_mode": "optional: TREND_FOLLOW|MEAN_REVERSION|BREAKOUT|RISK_OFF|NONE", "regime_assessment": "optional: TRENDING|RANGING|TRANSITIONAL|UNKNOWN"}]}}

most_impactful_headline.excerpt: The addition is the first crypto company to be licensed by the Securities and Futures Commission since June 2025, when the regulator approved Hong Kong BGE.

top_headlines_used.excerpt: Lawmakers want to make it illegal for any party in the EU to transact with Russian counterparties using crypto, to help enforce sanctions.

most_impactful_headline.title: Hong Kong regulator adds Victory Fintech to list of approved trading platforms
most_impactful_headline.excerpt: The addition is the first crypto company to be licensed by the Securities and Futures Commission since June 2025, when the regulator approved Hong Kong BGE.

top_headlines_used.title: Hong Kong regulator adds Victory Fintech to list of approved trading platforms

top_headlines_used.title: EU Moves to Ban All Crypto Transactions with Russian Entities: Report
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Lawmakers want to make it illegal for any party in the EU to transact with Russian counterparties using crypto, to help enforce sanctions.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin accumulation wave puts $80K back in play: Analyst
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Demand from Bitcoin accumulation addresses reached a new high, with analysts citing a futures market CME gap as a prediction point for their higher short-term price targets.

top_headlines_used.title: ETH chart pattern projects rally to $2.5K if key conditions are met: Data
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Ether is down 20% in February, but a developing bullish setup below $2,000 and growing upside liquidation clusters hint at a quick rebound.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin on Pace for Longest Losing Streak Since 2018 Bear Market
top_headlines_used.excerpt: The selling simply won't stop. If February closes red, Bitcoin will register five consecutive red months, the longest streak in seven years.

most_impactful_headline.title: Hong Kong regulator adds Victory Fintech to list of approved trading platforms
most_impactful_headline.excerpt: The addition is the first crypto company to be licensed by the Securities and Futures Commission since June 2025, when the regulator approved Hong Kong BGE.

top_headlines_used.title: Hong Kong regulator adds Victory Fintech to list of approved trading platforms
top_headlines_used.excerpt: The addition is the first crypto company to be licensed by the Securities and Futures Commission since June 2025, when the regulator approved Hong Kong BGE.

top_headlines_used.title: EU Moves to Ban All Crypto Transactions with Russian Entities: Report
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Lawmakers want to make it illegal for any party in the EU to transact with Russian counterparties using crypto, to help enforce sanctions.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin accumulation wave puts $80K back in play: Analyst
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Demand from Bitcoin accumulation addresses reached a new high, with analysts citing a futures market CME gap as a prediction point for their higher short-term price targets.

top_headlines_used.title: ETH chart pattern projects rally to $2.5K if key conditions are met: Data
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Ether is down 20% in February, but a developing bullish setup below $2,000 and growing upside liquidation clusters hint at a quick rebound.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin on Pace for Longest Losing Streak Since 2018 Bear Market
top_headlines_used.excerpt: The selling simply won't stop. If February closes red, Bitcoin will register five consecutive red months, the longest streak in seven years.

top_headlines_used.title: EU Moves to Ban All Crypto Transactions with Russian Entities: Report
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Lawmakers want to make it illegal for any party in the EU to transact with Russian counterparties using crypto, to help enforce sanctions.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin accumulation wave puts $80K back in play: Analyst
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Demand from Bitcoin accumulation addresses reached a new high, with analysts citing a futures market CME gap as a prediction point for their higher short-term price targets.

top_headlines_used.title: ETH chart pattern projects rally to $2.5K if key conditions are met: Data
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Ether is down 20% in February, but a developing bullish setup below $2,000 and growing upside liquidation clusters hint at a quick rebound.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin on Pace for Longest Losing Streak Since 2018 Bear Market
top_headlines_used.excerpt: The selling simply won't stop. If February closes red, Bitcoin will register five consecutive red months, the longest streak in seven years.

most_impactful_headline.title: Hong Kong regulator adds Victory Fintech to list of approved trading platforms
most_impactful_headline.excerpt: The addition is the first crypto company to be licensed by the Securities and Futures Commission since June 2025, when the regulator approved Hong Kong BGE.

top_headlines_used.title: Hong Kong regulator adds Victory Fintech to list of approved trading platforms
top_headlines_used.excerpt: The addition is the first crypto company to be licensed by the Securities and Futures Commission since June 2025, when the regulator approved Hong Kong BGE.

top_headlines_used.title: EU Moves to Ban All Crypto Transactions with Russian Entities: Report
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Lawmakers want to make it illegal for any party in the EU to transact with Russian counterparties using crypto, to help enforce sanctions.

top_headlines_used.title: ETH chart pattern projects rally to $2.5K if key conditions are met: Data
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Ether is down 20% in February, but a developing bullish setup below $2,000 and growing upside liquidation clusters hint at a quick rebound.

top_headlines_used.title: Logan Paul sells Pokémon card for $16.5M, years after fractional NFT row
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Paul once fractionalized ownership of the rare Pokémon card on Liquid Marketplace in 2022 before the website went offline, leading to a lawsuit as investors demanded returns.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin on Pace for Longest Losing Streak Since 2018 Bear Market
top_headlines_used.excerpt: The selling simply won't stop. If February closes red, Bitcoin will register five consecutive red months, the longest streak in seven years.

most_impactful_headline.title: Stablecoins gain ground for paychecks and daily spending: BVNK report
most_impactful_headline.excerpt: A global survey of 4,658 crypto users found 39% receive income in stablecoins and 27% use them for payments, with stronger adoption in emerging markets.

top_headlines_used.excerpt: BofA's February survey shows investor positioning in the U.S. dollar has fallen to its most negative level since at least early 2012.

top_headlines_used.title: Crypto sentiment hits extreme fear as Matrixport flags possible bottom
top_headlines_used.excerpt: With Bitcoin sentiment at four-year lows, analysts have flagged historic oversold signals and potential seller exhaustion.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin on Pace for Longest Losing Streak Since 2018 Bear Market
top_headlines_used.excerpt: The selling simply won't stop. If February closes red, Bitcoin will register five consecutive red months, the longest streak in seven years.

top_headlines_used.excerpt: Bitcoin's long-term holders show weakening accumulation, with on-chain data pointing to $54,000 as the next support if $65,000 breaks.

most_impactful_headline.title: Stablecoins gain ground for paychecks and daily spending: BVNK report
most_impactful_headline.excerpt: A global survey of 4,658 crypto users found 39% receive income in stablecoins and 27% use them for payments, with stronger adoption in emerging markets.

top_headlines_used.title: BofA survey flags dollar bearish bets at over a decade high. Here's what it means for bitcoin
top_headlines_used.excerpt: BofA's February survey shows investor positioning in the U.S. dollar has fallen to its most negative level since at least early 2012.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin on Pace for Longest Losing Streak Since 2018 Bear Market
top_headlines_used.excerpt: The selling simply won't stop. If February closes red, Bitcoin will register five consecutive red months, the longest streak in seven years.

top_headlines_used.title: Crypto sentiment hits extreme fear as Matrixport flags possible bottom
top_headlines_used.excerpt: With Bitcoin sentiment at four-year lows, analysts have flagged historic oversold signals and potential seller exhaustion.

top_headlines_used.title: Bitcoin’s Long-Term Holders Show Signs of Strain After February Sell-Off
top_headlines_used.excerpt: Bitcoin's long-term holders show weakening accumulation, with on-chain data pointing to $54,000 as the next support if $65,000 breaks.
